  "description": "Welcome to Terrazas de Bahía Casares, a newly renovated 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom apartment offering bright, modern comfort with panoramic sea views. Perched on a peaceful hillside just a short drive from the beach, this stylish retreat is part of a well-maintained gated community surrounded by lush greenery and coastal tranquility.\n\nInside, the apartment boasts a fresh contemporary design, with an open-plan living and dining area that flows out to a spacious terrace—perfect for morning coffee or sunset dinners with sweeping views of the Mediterranean. Both the living room and master bedroom enjoy direct sea views, filling the space with natural light and coastal energy. The fully equipped kitchen and two sleek bathrooms complete the home’s practical yet elegant feel.\n\nGuests have access to multiple swimming pools throughout the community, some of which are beautifully set with panoramic views of the sea and hills. Whether you're lounging poolside, relaxing on the terrace, or heading down to the beach just minutes away, Terrazas de Bahía Casares offers a peaceful escape with the best of the Costa del Sol within easy reach.",
